1. any non member(guest) can search and view question
2. member should be able to post new question
3. member should be able to add an answer
4. member can upvote a question , answer or comment
5. member can flag a question , answer or comment for serious problem or moderator attention
6. member will earn badges
7. member can add comments to any question or answer
8. member can vote to delete or close any question
9. moderator can close a question or undelete an already deleted question